# requests.http

### Get all coffee drinkers
GET http://coffee.jade.rip/drinkers

### Get Coffee Drinker by ID
GET http://coffee.jade.rip/drinker/id/1

### Get Coffee Drinker by name
GET http://coffee.jade.rip/drinker/name/Bob

### Get Coffee Drinker by name
GET http://coffee.jade.rip/drinker/name/jade

### Post a new coffee drinker
POST http://coffee.jade.rip/drinkers
Content-Type: application/json

  {
    "name": "Johnny",
    "favorite_drink_cost": 3.25,
    "favorite_drink_name": "White Mocha"
  }
### Update a coffee drinker
PUT http://coffee.jade.rip/drinkers/7
Content-Type: application/json

  {
    "favorite_drink_cost": 3.25,
    "favorite_drink_name": "White Mocha"
  }
### Delete a coffee drinker
DELETE http://coffee.jade.rip/drinkers/8

### Get all coffee drinkers
GET http://coffee.jade.rip/drinkers

### Post reset all coffee drinkers balances
POST http://coffee.jade.rip/reset-balances

### Post a new round of drinking coffee
POST http://coffee.jade.rip/coffee-rounds

